# Axodus Ecosystem Status

Last updated: 2026-06-04

Primary source of truth for maturity: `.instructions/NUCLEUS_MATURITY_REGISTER.md`

Framework: `.instructions/NUCLEUS_MATURITY_FRAMEWORK.md`

Current phase: RECAST 01 - Nucleus Maturity Audit & Baseline Register.

## Portfolio Summary

- Total nuclei audited: 15 including Global Docs / Instructions.
- Average maturity level: 3.60.
- Highest maturity level: L5.
- Lowest maturity level: L1.
- No nucleus is production-ready.
- Governance is HOLD / PILOT COMPLETE / BACKLOG CONTROLLED.
- Global docs are workspace-local because `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository.

## Current Nucleus Status

| Nucleus | Level | Portfolio State | Production Status | Next Work |
|---|---:|---|---|---|
| ACS | L5 | HOLD | Production forbidden | Tenant-scoped receipts/backtest planning only. |
| Academy | L4 | ADVANCE | Production reward/credentialing blocked | DB schema planning and full validation when approved. |
| AxodusAPP | L4 | ADVANCE | Production execution disabled | Balanced read-only contract alignment. |
| BBA-Agency | L2 | RECOVER | Production claims blocked | Define non-production validation and claim-review gate. |
| Business | L4 | ADVANCE | Persistence/execution blocked | Validation evidence and repository contract review. |
| Core | L5 | BACKLOG | Execution authority forbidden | Consumer pilot review after allocation. |
| Defi | L4 | ADVANCE | Fund movement blocked | Governance execution and custody decision planning only. |
| Dex | L3 | BACKLOG | Swaps/routing/settlement disabled | DEX backlog continuation for read-only route metadata/interface work. |
| Documentation | L4 candidate | RECOVER | Publication not approved | REQ-07 draft content corrections complete with warnings; REQ-08 content quality validation pending. |
| Governance | L5 | HOLD | Production execution blocked | Backlog control and validation maintenance only. |
| Lottery | L2 | BACKLOG | Randomness/prize/payout blocked | Instructions hygiene and validation report. |
| Marketplace | L5 | ADVANCE | Settlement/minting/value transfer blocked | Validation gate, API/runtime contract reconciliation, and app alignment. |
| Mining | L3 | ADVANCE | Provider/payout blocked | Validation report and provider evidence planning. |
| Trading | L4 | HOLD | Live trading/withdrawals blocked | Vault/KMS, local E2E discipline, and vendor ownership planning only. |
| Global Docs / Instructions | L1 -> L2 evidence created | RECOVER | Not applicable | Coordinator decision required for official versioning home. |

## Global Production Boundary

Production execution, treasury movement, wallet signing, on-chain writes, live trading, DEX swaps, settlement, marketplace minting/value transfer, mining payouts, lottery randomness/prize/payout, and production credentials remain disabled or gated across the ecosystem.

